data.description: Welcome to a beautiful home in Sierra Estates in Lockwood. Almost one half acre spacious lot!! Picture this, it’s a sunny winter afternoon. You pull into your driveway after a busy day of work and park your car. The first thing you notice as you step out of the car is just how peaceful the neighborhood is! From your driveway, you look across the street onto a serene open field. You can’t believe you are still in Billings, just 10-15 minutes from shopping and dining, and yet it feels like you are out in the country! As you walk into the house and walk up the stairs, you are greeted by the spacious living space. You pour a glass of wine in the open kitchen and step onto the balcony and look onto your large yard. You can’t believe this is your home…life is good! Sparkling clean and ready to move in! Wonderful RV parking too!!
